snippet.title: Divisibility Rules for 1, 2, 4, 5, 6, 8, 10, 12, ... (Tanton Mathematics)
snippet.description: The final video in the suite of divisibility rules. We've done the hard rules (3, 9, 11, 7, 13, 47, 241, etc). Now it is time to make sure we understand the less hard ones too!
